This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes novel data augmentation techniques for deep reinforcement learning. It is also likely to belong to cs.RO (Robotics) as the proposed techniques are aimed at improving adaptive robot control. Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as reinforcement learning is a subfield of AI. The paper also mentions the use of reflectional symmetries, which suggests it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper's focus on adaptive robot control suggests it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
